    "rich_text_UfhrYx": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_Xe87LQ": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "\"HOW CAN YOU AFFORD TO OFFER UNLIMITED REPLACEMENTS?\"",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_xXxLaU": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>This is the question we get asked the most. The honest answer is that we're so confident in the quality of our t-shirts that we know for the most part, we'll never have to replace them. </p><p></p><p>If we had any doubt in the quality of our tees, we wouldn't offer this.</p>"
          }
        },
        "button_XtHDTz": {
